Description: An excellent condition 2017 PRS SE Custom 24 in Whale Blue with upgraded American HFS and Vintage Bass pickups. All pots and wiring upgraded and with the PRS American pickups this sounds REALLY GOOD! I like this SE as much as my Core model PRS. The original owner said this about his mods he made to this guitar;... upgraded with a 5 way super (blade) switch (to remove the push/pull pot and still have split coil ability), kinman treble bleed kit premium cts pots and switchcraft input.
